  "faq_summary": [
    {
      "q": "What is the cheapest LLM API in 2026?",
      "a": "DeepSeek v4-flash at $0.14 input / $0.28 output per 1M tokens with 1M context. Among the big three US providers, Gemini 2.5 Flash-Lite is lowest at $0.10 / $0.40."
    },
    {
      "q": "Why is Claude Sonnet 5 priced at $2/$10 only until August 31, 2026?",
      "a": "It is introductory pricing. From September 1, 2026, Sonnet 5 costs $3/$15 per 1M tokens — a pre-announced 50% increase."
    },
    {
      "q": "Are per-token prices directly comparable across providers?",
      "a": "Only approximately. Anthropic's newest models tokenize the same text into roughly 30% more tokens than earlier Claude models, so identical sticker prices can produce different invoices. Compare cost per task, not cost per token."
    },
    {
      "q": "Do these prices include long-context surcharges?",
      "a": "No — base tiers only. Google and xAI roughly double rates above 200K-token prompts; Anthropic bills its 1M context at standard rates."
    },
    {
      "q": "How often is this table updated?",
